text: Marcelo Fernández (born 13 February 1967) is an Argentine rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
